This is a set of framed originals featuring the Five Platonic Solids and their corresponding Element. The Cube/Earth. The Octahedron/Air. The Tetrahedron/Fire. The Icosahedron/Water. And The Dodecahedron/Aether/Spirit. •
•
•
✍🏼With frames they measure 7x7inches. Wooden dark green frames (it looks great with the drawings). The drawings were made by hand with sharpie and prismacolor markers. Each is signed on the back of the frame and drawing itself. •
•
•
•
I can say this on the study of geometry and the platonic solids: “Liber enim librum aperit” (one book opens another) —Rhazes (ar-Razi). •
•
•
Id love to find a home for the entire set. I would rather not sell them individually. 🖤
